author: News Tribune
title: Prep Volleyball: Blair Oaks C team wins
text:
Share 
COLUMBIA — The Blair Oaks C team ended its season on a high note Monday, defeating Hickman 25-22, 26-24. 
Claire Smith had six aces and eight assists, and Sydney Nivens had two blocks. Katelyn Weber had nine digs and four kills. Madalyn Temmen had six kills, and Kayle Hoelscher and Sydney Rackers each had three. 
The Lady Falcons end the season with a 15-5-2 record. ﻿
